'''樟脑丸'''（{{lang-en|'''Mothball'''}}），又称'''卫生球'''、'''卫生丸'''、'''防蛀球'''、'''臭蛋'''、'''臭丸'''，是一类用作[[杀虫剂|杀虫剂]]、[[除臭剂|除臭剂]]的球状固体，主要用于防治衣物中的虫害（主要是[[衣蛾|衣蛾]]）和防[[黴|黴]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Collecting and Preserving Insects and Mites: Tools and Techniques|url=http://www.ars.usda.gov/Main/site_main.htm?docid=10141&page=11|publisher=United States Department of  Agriculture - Agricultural Research Service|accessdate=2011-07-26|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512202522/http://www.ars.usda.gov/Main/site_main.htm?docid=10141&page=11|dead-url=no}}</ref>樟脑丸得名自[[樟树|樟树]]树干中含有的[[樟脑|樟脑]]。由于过去的卫生球很多使用[[萘|萘]]，此类卫生球又称作'''萘丸'''。<ref name=nathp/>

==成分==

虽然“樟脑丸”得名自樟脑，但是常见的樟脑丸经常使用其他物质：过去的卫生球使用[[易燃|易燃]]的[[萘|萘]]与[[萘酚|萘酚]]，因此又稱為萘丸；<ref name=nathp>{{cite web|title=Naphthalene|url=http://npic.orst.edu/ingred/naphth.html|website=npic.orst.edu|accessdate=2017-11-26|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020125721/http://www.npic.orst.edu/ingred/naphth.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>现在则大部分被[[对二氯苯|对二氯苯]]所取代。这两种物质都有一种强烈的怪异甜气味，也就是所谓的“卫生球味”。相比之下，樟脑的气味有清凉感。<ref name=bce-camp/>这两种固体和樟脑一样，都直接[[升华|升华]]成为气体，对蛾子、其幼虫及人有毒。

使用萘和对二氯苯的樟脑丸不可共用，不然可能永久损伤想要保存的物品。<ref>{{cite web|title=Collecting and Preserving Insects and Mites: Tools and Techniques|url=http://www.ars.usda.gov/Main/site_main.htm?docid=10141&page=11|publisher=United States Department of  Agriculture - Agricultural Research Service|accessdate=2011-06-26|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512202522/http://www.ars.usda.gov/Main/site_main.htm?docid=10141&page=11|dead-url=no}}</ref>

使用樟脑的樟脑丸一般称为“天然樟脑丸”，而使用萘和对二氯苯等石油化工品的樟脑丸则经常称为“合成樟脑丸”；樟脑这种物质本身也可以由[[松节油|松节油]]合成制得。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Gubelmann|first1=I.|last2=Elley|first2=H. W.|title=American Production of Synthetic Camphor from Turpentine|journal=Industrial & Engineering Chemistry|date=1934-06|volume=26|issue=6|pages=589–594|doi=10.1021/ie50294a002}}</ref><ref name=bce-camp>{{cite journal|author1=赵振东|author2=毕良武|title=合成樟脑行业发展现状分析|journal=生物质化学工程|date=2009-07|volume=43|issue=4|pages=1-8|url=http://www.bce.ac.cn/CN/Y2009/V43/I4/1|accessdate=2017-11-26|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611213134/http://www.bce.ac.cn/CN/Y2009/V43/I4/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>天然樟脑丸的密度稍小于水，而合成樟脑丸则会沉于水底。<ref name=bce-camp/>

同样用于防黴防蛀的樟脑制品还有[[香樟|香樟]]木块、[[樟树|樟树]]球等。

==用途==
除了用于杀灭衣蛾、[[蠹魚|蠹魚]]之类的昆虫之外，含萘樟脑丸可以用于驱赶蝙蝠，防止其在阁楼中安营扎寨。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bat Repellent Natural Home Remedy|url=http://www.batsintheattic.org/repellent.html|website=www.batsintheattic.org|access-date=2017-11-26|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813010448/http://www.batsintheattic.org/repellent.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>有些人使用樟脑丸驱赶蛇、老鼠和松鼠，但也有研究指出樟脑丸并无此效果.<ref name="NPIC-Snakes">{{cite web|title=Snakes In and Around the House|url=http://npic.orst.edu/pest/snake.html|website=N?IC|publisher=National Pesticide Information Center|accessdate=2016-02-21|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303141856/http://npic.orst.edu/pest/snake.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NPI-Garden">{{cite web|title=Problem Wildlife in the Garden and Yard|url=http://npic.orst.edu/pest/wildyard.html|website=N?IC|publisher=National Pesticide Information Center|accessdate=2016-02-21|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023014256/http://www.npic.orst.edu/pest/wildyard.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NPIC-Wild>{{cite web|title=Problem Wildlife in the House|url=http://npic.orst.edu/pest/wildhouse.html|work=N?IC|publisher=National Pesticide Information Center|accessdate=2013-05-24|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020015030/http://www.npic.orst.edu/pest/wildhouse.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>樟脑丸可以危害宠物和小孩，因此大部分标识都要求放在封闭容器中使用。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vYo8rdgNte0C|title=Uncommon Uses for Common Household Products|publisher=Frank W. Cawood and Associates|year=2000|page=126|ISBN=1-890957-39-9|access-date=2017-11-26|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806022741/https://books.google.com/books?id=vYo8rdgNte0C|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[直线竞速赛|直线竞速赛]]选手使用将萘制樟脑丸溶解进[[汽油|汽油]]，再过滤出未溶解的固体，以期提高其[[辛烷值|辛烷值]]。[[流言终结者|流言终结者]]的《Scuba Diver, Car Capers》（2004）一集指出，萘丸大约的确可以提高汽车的[[马力|马力]]。

萘和对二氯苯曾用于制作{{tsl|en|Urinal deodorizer block|小便池除臭块|小便池中的除臭块}}。<ref name=Ross>{{Cite book | last1 = Rossberg | first1 = M. | last2 = Lendle | first2 = W. | last3 = Pfleiderer | first3 = G. | last4 = Tögel | first4 = A. | last5 = Dreher | first5 = E. L. | last6 = Langer | first6 = E. | last7 = Rassaerts | first7 = H. | last8 = Kleinschmidt | first8 = P. | last9 = Strack | first9 = H. | last10 = Cook | first10 = R. | last11 = Beck | first11 = U. | last12 = Lipper | first12 = K.-A. | last13 = Torkelson | first13 = T.R.| last14 = Löser | first14 = E. | last15 = Beutel | first15 = K.K. | last16 = Mann | first16 = T. | doi = 10.1002/14356007.a06_233.pub2 | chapter = Chlorinated Hydrocarbons | title = Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry | year = 2006 | isbn = 3527306730 | pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref>

==安全==
成人食入2克樟脑即可引发严重中毒，食入4克可致命。<ref name="mono-camp">{{cite web | publisher = International Programme on Chemical Safety | title = Poisons Information Monograph: Camphor | url = http://www.inchem.org/documents/pims/pharm/camphor.htm | access-date = 2017-11-26 | archive-date = 2021-02-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210211082914/http://www.inchem.org/documents/pims/pharm/camphor.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>萘的致死剂量估计在1-2克左右。对二氯苯的毒性较萘低，成人可以承受20克的口服剂量。

[[美国卫生及公共服务部|美国卫生及公共服务部]]认为，对二氯苯可以“合理推定为[[致癌物质|致癌物质]]”。对二氯苯在动物中可以致癌，但尚未在人类中进行大规模的研究。<ref name=ToxFAQ-Dichlor>{{cite web|title=ToxFAQs™ for Dichlorobenzenes|url=http://www.atsdr.cdc.gov/toxfaqs/tf.asp?id=703&tid=126|work=Toxic Substances Portal|publisher=Agency for Toxic Substances and Disease Registry|accessdate=2013-05-24|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126191021/https://www.atsdr.cdc.gov/toxfaqs/tf.asp?id=703&tid=126|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{tsl|en|National Toxicology Program|美国国家毒性项目}}、[[国际癌症研究机构|国际癌症研究机构]]（IARC）和[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]都认为对二氯苯致癌。<ref name=MSDS-PDB>{{cite web|title=p-dichlorobenzene (1,4-dichlorobenzene) |url=http://www.lakeland.edu/AboutUs/MSDS/PDFs/548/1-4-Dichlorobeneze%20%28Enoz%29.pdf |work=Material Safety Data Sheet |accessdate=2013-05-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522114605/http://www.lakeland.edu/AboutUs/MSDS/PDFs/548/1-4-Dichlorobeneze%20(Enoz).pdf |archivedate=2013-05-22 }}</ref>

患有[[G6PD缺乏症|G6PD缺乏症]]（蠶豆症）的人不可接觸萘制成的樟脑丸，否則會誘發[[溶血反應|溶血反應]]。<ref name="pnod">{{cite book|last1=Olson|first1=R. Olson|title=Poisoning & drug overdose|date=2011|publisher=McGraw-Hill Medical|location=New York|isbn=9780071668330|edition=6th|url=http://accessmedicine.mhmedical.com/book.aspx?bookid=391|access-date=2017-11-26|archive-date=2020-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923160155/http://accessmedicine.mhmedical.com/book.aspx?bookId=391|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|at=111}}
<ref>Santucci K, Shah B. Association of naphthalene with acute hemolytic anemia. ''Acad Emerg Med.'' 2000 Jan;7(1):42-7.</ref>IARC将萘列为[[2B類致癌物|2B類致癌物]]，即“可能导致人类和动物产生癌症”。<ref name="IARC-Naph">{{cite web | title=IARC Monographs on the Evaluation of Carcinogenic Risks to Humans | work=Monographs on the Evaluation of Carcinogenic Risks to Humans, Some Traditional Herbal Medicines, Some Mycotoxins, Naphthalene and Styrene, Vol. 82 (2002) (p. 367) | url=http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Monographs/vol82/index.php | accessdate=2008-12-25 | archive-date=2016-03-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325100030/http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Monographs/vol82/index.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>IARC还指出，对萘的急性暴露会造成人类、大鼠、兔子、小鼠产生[[白内障|白内障]]；慢性暴露在其蒸汽中还可造成{{tsl|en|retinal hemorrhage|视网膜出血}}。<ref name=EPA-Naph>{{cite web |title=Naphthalene |url=http://www.epa.gov/ttnatw01/hlthef/naphthal.html |work=Air Toxics Web Site |publisher=US Environmental Protection Agency |accessdate=2013-05-24 |archive-date=2015-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510192546/http://www.epa.gov/ttnatw01/hlthef/naphthal.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>因此，欧盟自2008年起开始禁用萘丸。<ref name=Gray>{{cite news|last=Gray|first=Kerrina|title=Council warned against use of poisonous moth balls|url=http://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/10813745.Council_warns_against_use_of_poisonous_mothballs/|work=Your Local Guardian|publisher=Newsquest (London) Ltd.|accessdate=2012-11-23|date=2013-11-17|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202233119/http://www.yourlocalguardian.co.uk/news/10813745.Council_warns_against_use_of_poisonous_mothballs/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Alderson>{{cite news|last=Alderson|first=Andrew|title=Holy straight bananas – now the Eurocrats are banning moth balls|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/howaboutthat/3463893/Holy-straight-bananas-now-the-Eurocrats-are-banning-moth-balls.html|accessdate=2013-11-23|newspaper=The Telegraph|date=2008-11-15|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103102921/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/howaboutthat/3463893/Holy-straight-bananas-now-the-Eurocrats-are-banning-moth-balls.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]自1993年起就停止生产、销售萘丸，并提倡使用樟脑取代。<ref>{{cite web|title=国务院经济贸易办公室、卫生部关于停止生产 和销售萘丸提倡使用樟脑制品的通知|url=http://www.people.com.cn/item/flfgk/gwyfg/1993/232101199301.html|website=www.people.com.cn|accessdate=2017-11-26|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20171008093257/www.people.com.cn/item/flfgk/gwyfg/1993/232101199301.html|archivedate=2017-10-08}}</ref>

[[科羅拉多大學波德分校|科羅拉多大學波德分校]]的研究人员使用[[秀麗隱桿線蟲|秀麗隱桿線蟲]]作为模型，指出了两种合成樟脑丸致癌的可能机理。<ref>[http://www.physorg.com/news70042017.html "Scientists May Have Solved Mystery Of Carcinogenic Mothballs"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.physorg.com/news70042017.html |date=20081010152244 }}, ''Physorg.com'', June 20, 2006.</ref><ref name=EHANS>{{cite web|title=Mothballs, air fresheners and cancer|url=http://www.environmentalhealth.ca/mothballsairfresh.htm|work=Environmental Health Association of Nova Scotia|publisher=Environmental Health Association of Nova Scotia|accessdate=2013-05-24|archive-date=2020-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222225028/http://www.environmentalhealth.ca/mothballsairfresh.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

萘和对二氯苯都会造成肠胃不适。<ref name="pnod">{{cite book|last1=Olson|first1=R. Olson|title=Poisoning & drug overdose|date=2011|publisher=McGraw-Hill Medical|location=New York|isbn=9780071668330|edition=6th|url=http://accessmedicine.mhmedical.com/book.aspx?bookid=391}}</ref>{{rp|at=111}}对二氯苯有神经毒性：<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Dubey|first1=Divyanshu|last2=Sharma|first2=Vibhash D.|last3=Pass|first3=Steven E.|last4=Sawhney|first4=Anshudha|last5=Stüve|first5=Olaf|title=-dichlorobenzene toxicity – a review of potential neurotoxic manifestations|journal=Therapeutic Advances in Neurological Disorders|date=2014-02-24|volume=7|issue=3|pages=177–187|doi=10.1177/1756285614521889|pmc=3994922}}</ref>一些青年会娱乐性地吸入对二氯苯，造成类似酒醉的神经毒性症状。<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/5219646.stm "Mothball sniffing warning issued"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/5219646.stm |date=20201127045018 }}, ''BBC News'', 27 July 2006.</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Feuillet|first1=L|last2=Mallet|first2=S|last3=Spadari|first3=M|title=Twin girls with neurocutaneous symptoms caused by mothball intoxication.|journal=The New England journal of medicine|date=2006-07-27|volume=355|issue=4|pages=423-4|doi=10.1056/NEJMc060329|pmid=16870927}}</ref>

